I'm coming.

10
00:01:22,599 --> 00:01:25,351
- Do you want your medicine?
- Yes, my darling.

11
00:01:32,108 --> 00:01:33,943
Do you want to play a game?

12
00:01:35,904 --> 00:01:37,572
I'm waiting for Papa to come home.

13
00:01:41,034 --> 00:01:43,119
What do you think Papa does?

14
00:01:43,870 --> 00:01:45,079
He's a doctor.

15
00:01:46,873 --> 00:01:48,124
He heals people.

16
00:01:48,207 --> 00:01:50,043
Oh. No, no.

17
00:01:50,126 --> 00:01:53,171
Your Papa, he kills people.

18
00:01:53,713 --> 00:01:57,467
- No.
- Is that who you love? Murderers?

19
00:02:27,956 --> 00:02:32,335
Mama. Mama. Mama. Mama!

20
00:02:32,418 --> 00:02:34,003
Leave me be. Go play.

21
00:02:34,921 --> 00:02:36,422
Mama!

22
00:02:36,506 --> 00:02:37,507
Leave me alone!

23
00:03:01,239 --> 00:03:02,782
Mama!

24
00:19:22,010 --> 00:19:23,762
- Hello.
- Let the sheep out, kid.

25
00:19:23,845 --> 00:19:26,348
- Why?
- Because otherwise I'll kill you.

26
01:38:05,062 --> 01:38:06,647
If you hear anything what do you do?

27
01:38:08,190 --> 01:38:09,441
I hide.

28
01:38:10,567 --> 01:38:11,819
Very good.

29
01:38:14,613 --> 01:38:16,073
- Good night.
- Good night.

30
01:38:16,657 --> 01:38:18,534
- Say good night.
- Good night.

31
01:38:19,827 --> 01:38:20,953
Good night.

32
