Where are we going?

35
01:43:06,571 --> 01:43:08,657
We're going on an adventure, darling.
Hang on.

36
01:43:22,963 --> 01:43:23,964
Mama.

37
01:43:25,048 --> 01:43:26,383
A mosquito bite me.

38
01:43:27,217 --> 01:43:28,135
It's okay.

39
01:43:28,218 --> 01:43:30,637
Dou Dou, do you like mosquitoes?

40
01:43:51,158 --> 01:43:51,992
Mama.

41
01:43:52,075 --> 01:43:55,662
- Do mosquitoes have friends?
- I don't know.

42
01:43:59,916 --> 01:44:01,334
I don't think so.

43
01:44:16,975 --> 01:44:18,101
Hang on.

44
01:56:36,130 --> 01:56:39,217
Remember what I told you.
Don't touch anything. Okay?

45
01:58:11,517 --> 01:58:14,937
Remember what I told you.
I'll come looking for you. Okay?

46
