- What's going on?
- It's the equipment.

47
02:00:32,158 --> 02:00:33,617
The cameras are down.

48
02:00:34,535 --> 02:00:35,745
The whole lower sector.

49
02:00:35,828 --> 02:00:38,122
I'll restart the system.

50
02:13:10,540 --> 02:13:11,583
My Dou Dou.

51
02:15:42,984 --> 02:15:44,527
I lost my little Dou Dou.

52
02:15:52,702 --> 02:15:56,039
I looked for you all over.
Where were you?

53
02:15:56,122 --> 02:15:58,333
I hid like you told me.

54
02:16:00,418 --> 02:16:01,920
I love you.

55
02:16:02,420 --> 02:16:04,214
Me too. I love you.


